---

8. Testing

Test Cases Performed

Test Case	Expected Result	Status

Add valid expense	Added to list	Passed
Add invalid date	Shows error	Passed
Delete last entry	Removes last item	Passed
Budget check	Shows remaining/alert	Passed
Display screens	Show complete data	Passed
Set budget	Updates budget label	Passed



---

9. Conclusion

This project successfully implements a beginner-friendly money management tool.
It demonstrates:

GUI design

Event-driven programming

User input handling

Data presentation


The program can be further expanded using file storage, charts, or monthly reports.

